TITLE: Configuring Proxmox Provider with API Token Authentication
DESCRIPTION: Terraform configuration block for the Proxmox provider using API token authentication, SSH agent, and insecure connection. This establishes the connection to the Proxmox API.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bpg/terraform-provider-proxmox/blob/main/docs/index.md#2025-04-23_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: hcl
CODE:
```
provider "proxmox" {
  endpoint  = var.virtual_environment_endpoint
  api_token = "terraform@pve!provider=xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx"
  insecure  = true
  ssh {
    agent    = true
    username = "terraform"
  }
}
```

